CustomField.formula: IF(OR(CONTAINS(Inbound_Form_Fleet__c, "-"),CONTAINS(Inbound_Form_Fleet__c, "+")),IF(Or( Inbound_Form_Fleet__c ="21+", Inbound_Form_Fleet__c ="21 - 50", Inbound_Form_Fleet__c ="25 - 49", Inbound_Form_Fleet__c ="50+" ),1,IF(OR( Inbound_Form_Fleet__c ="3 - 50", Inbound_Form_Fleet__c ="10 - 24", Inbound_Form_Fleet__c ="N/A" ),0.5,IF(Inbound_Form_Fleet__c ="1 - 2",-1,0))),IF(VALUE(Inbound_Form_Fleet__c)>20,1,IF(Inbound_Form_Fleet__c ="1 - 2",-1,0)))
CustomField.label: Inbound Fleet Score
